{"tid":2201800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達：開跑冇耐個天行雷，有個男人喺我身邊講：「行雷啦，黃洋達你仲唔走？你成日搞亂香港，唔怕畀雷劈呀？」","createTime":"2020-09-14T05:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:09:54.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e83c46627283b1c1b3a457525c011dcb3585ea23","tid":2201800,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1TTkaU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1TTkaU.png&h=ec0146e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃洋達：<br />\n中午有雨，所以晏晝去睇戲，夜晚先跑。<br />\n開始跑冇耐，個天開始行雷閃電，有個男人喺我身邊，邊跑邊講：<br />\n「行雷啦，黃洋達你仲唔走？你成日搞亂香港，唔怕畀雷劈呀？」<br />\n條友一講完，自己就仆街，五體投地咁扒落地，成面鼻血。<br />\n我冇理佢繼續跑，全程行雷，但冇落雨，等我跑完先落，感恩～"},{"pid":"ba3c11c6f18aa5ff4b04730026a5df62594b1454","tid":2201800,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"黃洋達搞亂香港???<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1759a3fb2ed1bdc4f52fc3c502976e13d4ca6d","tid":2201800,"uid":196924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"黃洋達喎?<br />\n失蹤人口點樣搞亂香港?"},{"pid":"268ff1633e2dfc380e82961a487b6167988c3607","tid":2201800,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba3c11c6f18aa5ff4b04730026a5df62594b1454","tid":2201800,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"黃洋達搞亂香港???<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"佢真誠為港<br />\n永續基本法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6c5c6edb1048e329e5d92ea57e0804fb5aead4","tid":2201800,"uid":2471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"10000米.jpg"},{"pid":"f39501cbe83865c1abbb0769ad10b527bf02fac6","tid":2201800,"uid":128993,"li